{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":8653,"duration_api_ms":10063,"ttft_ms":8568,"ttft_stream_ms":2676,"time_to_request_ms":28,"num_turns":1,"result":"`const` binds a name to a value that can't be reassigned. `let` allows reassignment.\n\n```js\nlet x = 1;\nx = 2;       // fine\n\nconst y = 1;\ny = 2;       // TypeError\n```\n\nOne important nuance: `const` doesn't make the value immutable, just the binding. Objects and arrays declared with `const` can still be mutated:\n\n```js\nconst obj = { a: 1 };\nobj.a = 2;   // fine — mutating the object\nobj = {};    // TypeError — reassigning the binding\n```\n\nBoth are block-scoped (unlike `var`). Prefer `const` by default; use `let` only when you know you need to reassign.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"684b449b-50d8-4026-b261-2cbd8e5dadfd","total_cost_usd":0.0531869,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":7751,"cache_read_input_tokens":11393,"output_tokens":178,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":7751,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":3,"output_tokens":178,"cache_read_input_tokens":11393,"cache_creation_input_tokens":7751,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":7751},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":509,"outputTokens":15,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.000584,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":3,"outputTokens":178,"cacheReadInputTokens":11393,"cacheCreationInputTokens":7751,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.0526029,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"c963ff6d-d8f6-411b-9ea3-4a783887c12c